{"title":"故乡笨钟","authors":["杨献瑶"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":6,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡笨钟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨献瑶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的故乡有一口笨钟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人说，自从铸造了它"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就不曾有人把它敲响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说它比木头还蠢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比石头还笨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡忽然传来消息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说笨钟不敲自响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发出金子的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说它好象有一簇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比电子还灵敏的弦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人说，笨钟不鸣则已"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一鸣必有大喜我翘首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的家乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果然，两只白天鹅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞落碧波千顷的湖面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"久违了，故乡的笨钟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"久违了，不朽的先哲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉你，我骄傲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是你的子孙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我从远方奉上心香一瓣"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}